\par {\b CONNECTION OVERVIEW}
\par 
\par PowerBI Executive Dashboard (source application) connects to Exchange Online (target application) to analyze email communication patterns, meeting productivity metrics, and executive time allocation. This integration provides leadership insights into organizational communication efficiency and collaboration trends.
\par 
\par {\b APPLICATIONS INVOLVED}
\par 
\par {\b 1. PowerBI Executive Dashboard}
\par    - Platform: Power BI Premium workspace
\par    - Version: 4.1.2
\par    - Deployment: Microsoft 365 tenant
\par    - Refresh Schedule: Real-time and daily aggregations
\par 
\par {\b 2. Exchange Online}
\par    - Service: Microsoft 365 Exchange Online
\par    - Data Sources: Executive mailboxes, calendar data, meeting insights
\par    - Time Range: Rolling 12-month analysis window
\par    - Authentication: Service principal with certificate
\par 
